dcterms:description: A dataset consisting of 563 hematoxylin and eosin (H&E)-stained formalin-fixed paraffin-embedded (FFPE) whole-slide images of renal cell carcinoma (RCC) that have been de-identified and labeled with the predominant histological pattern of each image, including renal oncocytoma, chromophobe RCC, clear cell RCC, and papillary RCC.
dcterms:title: DHMC RCC Dataset
